ats' Green New Deal Wing Takes Shape Amid Wave Of Progressive Climate Hawk Wins|website=The Huffington Post|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181113101635/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/green-new-deal-progressive-democrats_us_5be26f5be4b0769d24c6a954|archive-date=13 November 2018|url-status=live|accessdate=13 November 2018|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last=Kinzel|first=Bob|date=19 February 2019|url=https://www.vpr.org/post/hes-2020-bernie-sanders-running-president-again|title=He's In For 2020: Bernie Sanders Is Running For President Again|agency=Vermont Public Radio|accessdate=25 November 2019|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last=Klar|first=Rebecca|date=10 June 2019|url=https://thehill.com/homenews/campaign-polls/447671-poll-socialism-gaining-in-popularity|title=Poll: Socialism gaining in popularity|newspaper=The Hill|accessdate=17 January 2020|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last=Knight|first=Ben|date=2 May 2019|url=https://www.dw.com/en/collectivization-remarks-split-german-social-democrats/a-48578188|title=Collectivization remarks split German Social Democrats|agency=Deutsche Welle|accessdate=8 February 2020|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last=Kristof|first=Nicholas|date=27 October 2011|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2011/10/27/opinion/kristof-crony-capitalism-comes-homes.html|title=Crony Capitalism Comes Home|newspaper=The New York Times|accessdate=1 March 2020|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last=Krugman|first=Paul|date=13 February 2020|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/13/opinion/bernie-sanders-socialism.html|title=Bernie Sanders Isn't a Socialist|newspaper=The New York Times|accessdate=23 February 2020|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last=Kvitrud|first=Erlend|date=29 June 2019|url=https://foreignpolicy.com/2019/06/29/what-the-right-gets-wrong-about-socialism/|title=What the Right Gets Wrong About Socialism|newspaper=Foreign Policy|accessdate=10 April 2020|ref=harv}}\n: {{cite news|last=Laqueur|first=Walter Z.|date=August 1976|url=https://www.commentarymagazine.com/articles/walt