mbers|accessdate=October 31, 2012|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130102140358/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/10/31/tuesday-final-ratings-dancing-with-the-stars-adjusted-down/155498/|archivedate=January 2, 2013}}</ref> \n |ShortSummary    = Kate and BJ are invited to Kate's handsome neighbor's Halloween party. Since Kate really likes him, BJ teaches her how to be more sexy and appealing. Meanwhile, Ben and Tommy decide to stay home to give out candy in hopes of meeting hot moms, but the night takes an unexpected twist when Tommy accidentally eats BJ's \"candy\" from Amsterdam. Later in the night, Kate meets Will ([[Geoff Stults]]), a single dad who shares the same personality traits as her.\n |LineColor       = 00C5CD\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 7\n |Title           = Career Day\n |DirectedBy      = [[Jay Chandrasekhar]]\n |WrittenBy       = [[Lorene Scafaria]]\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2012|11|13}}\n |ProdCode        = 1AVE06\n |Viewers         = 2.39<ref>{{cite web|last=Bibel|first=Sara|title=Tuesday Final Ratings: 'The Voice', 'Parenthood' & 'NCIS' Adjusted Up; 'Go On', 'Hart of Dixie', 'Happy Endings' & 'The Mindy Project' Adjusted Down|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/11/14/tuesday-final-ratings-the-voice-parenthood-go-on-hart-of-dixie-happy-endings-the-mindy-project-adjusted-down/157590/|work=TV by the Numbers|accessdate=November 14, 2012}}</ref> \n |ShortSummary    = Ben tries to pursue a career as a wine seller before he speaks at Maddie's career day at her school. Ben continually intrudes on Kate and Will's relationship. BJ feels she is not liked by the waiting staff at the bar.\n |LineColor       = 00C5CD\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 8\n |Title           = Reunion\n |DirectedBy      = [[Daisy von Scherler Mayer|Daisy Mayer]]\n |WrittenBy       = [[Lindsey Shockley]]\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2012|11|20}}\n |ProdCode        = 1AVE07\n |Viewers         = 2.35<ref>{{cite web|las